'''Ksar Hadada''' is a [[Wikipedia:ksar|ksar]] in southeastern [[Tunisia]]. Along with two other ksar's around [[Wikipedia:Tataouine|Tataouine]], Ksar Hadada was filmed for [[Mos Espa]]'s [[Slave Quarters Row/Legends|Slave Quarters]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].

The [[Wikipedia:Arabic language|Arabic]] spelling is: قصر حدادة‎. Sometimes it is spelled "Ksar Hedada".

